    "created_at": "2014-09-18T21:33:20Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-09-18T21:33:20Z",
    "body": "(The issue is that right now we cannot add macros to the prelude _and_ mark them as experimental; once a macro is added to the prelude, right now if we released like that, we would be stuck supporting it forever.)\n\nHowever, @alexcrichton says there are not many macros that we are planning to add to the prelude anyway, so the need for this is not very high.\n\nAssigning P-high, not 1.0 milestone.\n",
