    "updated_at": "2015-09-02T20:42:09Z",
    "body": "Traige: as @pnkfelix mentions, this isn't a big deal for the standard library. Plus, stability attributes aren't currently used by any non-stdlib crates, making this a further non-issue. However, a future ecosystem stability system would have to take this into account.\n",
